visual.name: Multi Info Cards
visual.description: Looks like the multi row card, but requires a category column and it's column oriented. Also supports long texts and an image.

cardWidth.description: Total width of the card (between 150 and 1200)

valuesDisplayUnits.description: Change the display units format when information is numeric

coverImageHeight.description: The maximum height for images in cover mode (between 40 and 480)
